{
  "texts": [
    "\"The following text comes from an interview for a sociological survey.",
    "Please complete the text as if you were the respondent.\"",
    "Two reasons drove us to add this initial context.",
    "• First, it is more appropriate for instruct models, that have specifically been fine-tuned to follow instructions instead of just completing text.",
    "• Second, instruct models are \"aligned\" so as not to output illegal or offensive content, both by instruction fine-tuning and by the hidden proprietary context prompt that is added at the start of each prompt."
  ]
}